item.description:
Up for a break from the weekend of eating and shopping? How about getting in a run at the Braintree High School Track? Join me while I get in time at the track for walk or jog of your own. Or use it as an excuse to get out of the house and too much family time for some "me" time. :)

We'll meet by the entrance to the track next to the bleachers. Late arrivals just start in at your own pace or catch up to others already on the track.


10am
Braintree HS Track
128 Town St
Braintree, MA
